metadata.name: Soul Dispersion
metadata.description:
Soul Dispersion is exhibited at M.A.D.S. Art Gallery for LIQUID ARSENAL Exhibiton in Milano, Italy and Fuerteventura, Spain. Also, exhibition can be available on metaverse.

Art Gallery: M.A.D.S. Art Gallery
Art Curator: Federica Acciarino
Date: May 28th - June 3rd

Concept: M.A.D.S. Gallery with Liquid
Arsenal stands as a manifestation of the will to reflect on the concept of "liquidity" and, at the same time, is configured as
a sort of walkway between reality - solid and tangible - and unreality - virtual, simulated, non-concrete.
